These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, romance
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, climbing
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel   |
| Sport         | climbing | cricket |
| Transport     | helicopter | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, mango
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, spy
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, ship
1. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | banana     | mango |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | sports  |
| Pet           | horse         | chinchilla     |
| Transport     | van   | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker
2 different pets are kept: bird, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the dressmaker##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | mirinda     | iced-tea |
| Job         | dressmaker | architect    |
| Pet         | bird         | snake        |
| Transport   | trike         | skateboard    |

