.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, juice
There 2 different types of food: spinach, corn
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, salsa
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person eating corn is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | tea |
| Food          | corn   | spinach  |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | hiking     |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | salsa         |

