.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, librarian
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, japanese
2 different pets are kept: rat, fish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
2. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
3. the librarian is the turkish##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | librarian | firefighter    |
| Nationality   | turkish       | japanese |
| Pet           | rat         | fish    |
| Sport         | sailing    | handball   |

